#category Logic Changes
/// No Teleporter Locks
///
/// Removes the skill requirements logic adds to locked teleporters.
/// Logic may force teleporting to Burrows without Bash, Depths without Glide, Reach without Flap and Wastes/Ruins/Willow without Burrow.
/// Note that this can sidestep key hints since Flap may be inside Reach etc.

!!set RemoveTPLocks
